tags.name: LT 28 Traffic Cameras/LT-56 Traffic Camera LHS panel

testSteps.description: Given I am at the LiveTraffic Website
When I click on the menu button
And I click "Traffic Cameras" button from the menu list

Then I should see list of Camera regions from All Cameras tab
| Camera_Region |
| Inner Sydney |
| Sydney North |
| Sydney West |
| Sydney South |
| Regional North |
| Regional South |
| All Regional |
| All NSW |
| All Sydney |
When I click "Regional South" button from All Cameras List
Then I should Camera Region name "Regional South" on page

Then I should see list of below cameras from "Regional South" region
| Camera_Locations |
| Kosciuszko Road (Wilson |
| M1 Princes Motorway (Mt Ousley) |
| Princes Highway (Albion Park Rail) |
| Princes Highway (Wollongong) |
| Princes Highway (Batemans Bay) |
| Princes Highway (Bulli) |
| Five Islands Road (Port Kembla) |
| Memorial Drive (Towradgi) |
| Shellharbour Road (Warilla) |
When I click back arrow button

Then I should see list of Camera regions from All Cameras tab
| Camera_Region |
| Inner Sydney |
| Sydney North |
| Sydney West |
| Sydney South |
| Regional North |
| Regional South |
| All Regional |
| All NSW |
| All Sydney |
